---
description: Product Design Constitution — four workflows, no hackathon dashboards
alwaysApply: true
---

product-design:

- Four product surfaces only: Workspace, Payments, Connectors, Profile.
- Never add pages for backend subsystems (Treasury, Signals, Weight, Radar, etc.).
- Every API integration must produce real user value — no fake metrics or decorative widgets.
- Progressive disclosure: simple default, "Why?" for evidence and technical depth.
- Live data over static cards. Honest status when services are not configured.
- See docs/PRODUCT-DESIGN-CONSTITUTION.md for full constitution.
